<p style="text-align:justify">One suite to complete the entire SEO workflow. Setup a Auto SEO Plugin in your website within minutes. Advertising India Plugin is a LSO based technology that adds a specific features which gives power to discovered and Manage your business online<br />
<br />
And Start Using Our Latest (LSO) Technology to discovered your website on Search engine Like Google, Yahoo etc</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">Local SEO is an excellent strategy to gain local clients and customers. We are the best local SEO service provider. Use our innovative approaches and ideas to gain a competitive advantage among local businesses.</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">Advertising India is a tech enabled disruptive startup with a vision to make all SMEs get discovered online throughout the world. Advertising India enables Small and Medium Businesses (SMEs) to create and maintain an online presence by simply using Smart Phone or the Web.<br />
<br />
Advertising India helps to connect online consumers to local offline businesses but along with more traffic by making your Website easy to find via Google. We ensure that if a potential customer is searching for your product via a mobile device our any other device in Google, then your relevant store which is closest to the customer appears in the result. Our customers uses ADVERTISING INDIA Auto SEO Plugin which is a web based technology that adds a specific features which gives Power to all Static or Dynamic web Pages to get discovered on Search engine Like Google, Yahoo etc.<br />
<br />
We do not make website, We get your business more customers by enabling your client to create a web presence via ePlugin, which is optimized to search engines, and incentivizes the customer to create content for their site by engaging them.<br />
<br />
Auto Seo plugin provides you with the following benefits:-<br />
1.     Discover your website online<br />
2.     Drive local relevant traffic to local offline stores (Local Search Optimization)<br />
3.     Be more visible on search engines for product & location based<br />
4.     Auto Optimize, Auto Prompt Content for Local Search<br />
5.     Search Track & analyze online consumer behavior<br />
6.     Compatible with static and dynamic Web Pages.<br />
7.     Update and Manage your Plugin via Web Portal.<br />
<br />
 A beautiful Website is nice, But a website that get Discovered is nicer. Create your Business plugin and get discovered your website by more potential customer in organic search result.<br />
<br />
Why LSO is Important ?<br />
Because it connects to the consumers locally who are searching online.</p>
